<p style="text-align: left;"><a name="thirtytwo"></a>[32] OP CIT table B</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a name="thirtythree"></a>[33] OP CIT, pg 92</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a name="thirtyfour"></a>[34] Bae Ji-sook, “Seoul Not Safe from Artillery Attack,” <em>Korea Times</em>, (November 26, 2010) at: <a href="http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2010/11/177_77036.html">http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2010/11/177_77036.html</a> (searched date: 17 June 2012)</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a name="thirtyfive"></a>[35] Seoul Metro website<a href="http://www.seoulmetro.co.kr/eng/page.jsp?code=A02000400000">http://www.seoulmetro.co.kr/eng/page.jsp?code=A02000400000</a> (searched date: 17 June 2012)</p>
